Title: Delver's Call: Mycomancer Cavern
Description:
Spice Help Needed!

Fungarians in the Mycomancer Caverns have been raiding spice crates bound for Lorel's Crossing. Someone needs to go into those caverns and push back the fungarian menace! 

Will pay well.
ObjectivesText: Complete the Mycomancer Cavern delve on any difficulty.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Return to Valrin Paller in Dunelle's Kindness
RewardText: I heard the fungarians had been thinned out by someone recently. Thank you!

Objectives.Text: Mycomancer Cavern delve completed on any difficulty
